const COMMON = `Repo: ${ROOT}. The sprint-ledger v2 redesign has LANDED in src/ and the repo's own ledger is migrated. Read these two files FIRST — they are the contract and the ground truth of what shipped:
1. ${DESIGN} (design; §8 tests, §9 docs are your requirements)
