tests/test_cli.py: add help smoke tests in the existing subprocess style: 'sprint complete --help' (assert '--commit' and '100%' or 'primary acceptance criteria'), 'sprint drop --help' (assert '--reason'), 'sprint --help' (assert 'state.yaml'), 'migrate sprint-ledger --help' (assert '--dry-run' and '--apply'), 'migrate --help' (assert 'sprint-ledger').
tests/CLAUDE.md: add missing Test Map rows for tests/test_sprint.py, tests/test_generate_html.py and the two NEW files tests/test_sprint_migrate.py + tests/test_sprint_parallel.py (they are being written concurrently by another agent — describe them from the design §8, do not open them). Keep table formatting.
Note: only run pytest on tests/test_generate_html.py and the specific new test_cli.py tests (-k); the concurrent agents own the other files.`,
  },
]

phase('Docs')
const docs = [
