  },
  {
    key: 'D2-claude-agents-arch',
    prompt: `${COMMON}

YOUR FILES: docs/architecture.md, src/decree/CLAUDE.md, src/decree/commands/AGENTS.md, CLAUDE.md (repo root), AGENTS.md (repo root) ONLY. Do NOT touch tests/CLAUDE.md (owned by another agent).
