YOUR FILES: skills/decree-ddd/SKILL.md, src/decree/templates/agent/skills/decree-ddd/SKILL.md, docs/plans/2026-06-26-sprint-scoped-execution-handoff.md (banner line only), NEW docs/plans/2026-07-03-parallel-safe-sprint-ledger.md, NEW changelog.d/+sprint-ledger-v2.breaking.md, NEW changelog.d/+sprint-complete.feature.md ONLY.
